        <para id="id3221991">First, put them into alphabetical order, for clarity.</para>
        <para id="id3221996">[LO 5.1.1]</para>
        <para id="id3707078">Now, in <emphasis effect="bold">YOUR </emphasis>view, choose the SIX <emphasis effect="bold">BEST</emphasis> qualities, which you think can lead to a happy life.</para>
        <list id="id12618537" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Write down <emphasis effect="bold">YOUR</emphasis> list</item>
        </list>
        <list id="id4225809" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>NOW, examine, CLOSELY, which SIX you have chosen. </item>
        </list>
        <list id="id4263426" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Let your educator show you what the other learners have chosen.</item>
          <item/>
        </list>
        <list id="id11570100" list-type="bulleted">
          <item/>
          <item>Now YOU need to decide what ACTIONS SHOW these values; to find examples of how these values are manifest in society.</item>
