        <list id="id11834253" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Now ask yourself whether <emphasis effect="bold">YOU </emphasis>act like this. (TIP: It is impossible to be perfect in all categories).</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id13720660">If you already <emphasis effect="bold">DO </emphasis>act like this, then choose ANOTHER six and go through the process again. </para>
        <para id="id11883728">If you <emphasis effect="bold">DO NOT </emphasis>act like this, then ask yourself what you need to DO to act like this.</para>
        <para id="id8111481">Remember, <emphasis effect="bold">YOU</emphasis> are making the decisions and coming to <emphasis effect="bold">YOUR OWN</emphasis> conclusions.</para>
        <para id="id11809048">In other words, <emphasis effect="bold">YOU</emphasis> are selecting a way of life; a FUTURE way to behave: <emphasis effect="bold">A VALUE SYSTEM.</emphasis></para>
