      <section id="id11294488">
        <title>[LO 2.1]</title>
        <para id="id11770906">This time you will be looking at how a person is judged.</para>
        <para id="id11921385">You know that most characters are judged, at face value, on:</para>
        <para id="id13630437">the way they behave;</para>
        <para id="id11872427">the way they talk; </para>
        <para id="id11872432">what they talk about;</para>
        <para id="id12596244">their relationships with those about them</para>
        <list id="id10171898" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>HOW DO <emphasis effect="bold">YOU</emphasis> RATE? </item>
          <item>MY judgement of . . .</item>
        </list>
        <list id="id4235908" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>The way I behave</item>
          <item>The way I talk </item>
          <item>What I talk about</item>
          <item>How I get on with those about me? </item>
        </list>
      </section>
